                <h2>Who can Use</h2>
                <p>The targeted audiences for Parents Banking Application are the account owner (parent) and account recipient (child).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2>How to Use</h2>
                <p>Sign In/Log In as an account owner (parent) to access your multiple Bank account and manage transactions or as an account recipient (child) to create a wishlist</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
